XMLV: Invesco S&P MidCap Low Volatility ETF

The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its total assets in the securities that comprise the underlying index. Strictly in accordance with its guidelines and mandated procedures, S&P Dow Jones Indices LLC compiles, maintains and calculates the index, which is designed to measure the performance of a subset of approximately 80 securities in the S&P MidCap 400 Â® Index that have the lowest realized volatility over the past 12 months.
